Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:13.12,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby, Ruby.....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:15.53,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:19.49,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:23.52,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:28.44,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Pain, pain, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:31.11,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Is there really a spell like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.55,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I am a magic expert!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.26,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that only for grown up witches?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.11,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,I am-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:43.24,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on you guys... my wounds aren't that deep, I should be fine in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.12,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, see, you {\i1}are{\i0} pushing yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.26,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:51.17,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.04,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake now, Ruby-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:57.40,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:10.20,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this your share.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.86,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, there's enough for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:17.70,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Using something like this to win me over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.18,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.47,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to hear your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:22.34,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,My story?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:22.86,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:25.89,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,About that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:35.96,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,What... that hill has long since been the refuge of us witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:40.41,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,We were without conflict, and lived peacefully amongst ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:43.17,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, they just barged in selfishly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:49.07,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Causing unnecessary destruction, doing this so-called development for their own selfish reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:54.23,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,They laid waste, broke down, and ruined everything! {not sure about the 3rd verb..."Arashi magutte, kowashi magutte, (umichishi)ni magutteru!"} {fumichirashi?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:56.40,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,The story about you cruel humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.77,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in listening to it now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.44,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.14,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.80,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,You can understand too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.25,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,About our own home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:11.90,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect the Witches' Hill, we have no choice but to destroy the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.00,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:18.19,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one left from our group...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:23.07,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it okay to kill everyone who's trying to take away the hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.88,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones I'm killing are humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.75,Yukihime,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans and Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.37,Yukihime,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the value of their lives that different?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.06,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with killing humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:37.49,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it fine to kill them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.64,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Those foolish humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:48.35,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there any other way? To live together without fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:51.45,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless. Doing anything at this point is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.24,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master will pass judgment on the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.89,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:59.47,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Judgment, eh? That sounds like quite an egotistical person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:03.57,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,To say that hurting others to accomplish your own goals is okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.06,Yukihime,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, aren't you guys doing things selfishly too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:08.06,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the same as the humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.23,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:11.35,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that how witches do things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.09,Yukihime,,0000,0000,0000,,Witches are scary, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.72,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Witches aren't scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.54,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, yeah, witch brats aren't scary {\i1}at all{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.75,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.10,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:23.43,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Once that hill is taken, I won't have any other place to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:27.17,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's all? If that's case, why doesn't Ruby-san just come to Youkai Academy also?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:31.87,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Although you might feel a bit homesick and lonesome,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.95,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,The student lifestyle is actually quite fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:35.71,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's study together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.20,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,And, after that, you can join the Newspaper Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.09,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Moka-san, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:43.21,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? There's gonna be two witches?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.75,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:47.14,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:49.02,Yukihime,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I {\i1}cool{\i0} your heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:53.20,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,But for me... I can no longer be anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.08,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.56,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:28.73,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't betray you ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.04,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Ruby-san went missing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:40.67,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:44.76,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.03,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:52.47,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.74,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:56.81,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get any further on this hill!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.00,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.47,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, there must be some other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:07.53,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right, Ruby-san! Let's think of it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.62,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:19.60,Bat,,0000,0000,0000,,There're man-eating plants underneath the sunflower field! {FUCK, YEAH! BAT SMASH}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:26.93,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are faithful servants created by the Master to protect this hill!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:30.34,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Back down, Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:41.70,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirayuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.02,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here, Tsukune-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.05,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.51,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only one witch brat, why are you panicking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.39,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.73,Yukihime,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone who touches Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:55.91,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirayuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.90,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.93,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.51,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let one finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:02.34,Yukihime,,0000,0000,0000,,...touch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:05.34,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Moka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.47,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:10.58,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Moka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:12.49,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:14.88,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.02,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut everyone to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:24.33,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.20,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.23,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.93,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my opponent is a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:36.13,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I can hear Moka-san's screams...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.25,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,But my legs won't even move...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:42.53,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Moka-san, please tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:47.49,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,What I can do... the things that a human can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:53.98,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.00,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.69,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.47,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,A vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.03,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Moka....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.52,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Moka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:33.41,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot... you're always overdoing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:35.74,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to you, I was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:37.67,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Moka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:50.41,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,Young fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:53.64,Bat,,0000,0000,0000,,This week's battle took one second... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:56.58,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.58,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:02.29,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,I will... protect the Witches' Hill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.11,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:08.10,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,and also, the Master's wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:11.98,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:16.59,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,They're bigger than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:19.86,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukune-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:25.93,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let Tsukune-san go, Ruby-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:40.32,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Master's desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:43.15,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Master's wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:46.02,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Master's ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:49.41,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this Master...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.87,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:57.96,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.49,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Moka-san? Hey wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:10.60,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari, Mizore! Please take care of Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:15.30,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukune-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.21,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:21.48,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:23.41,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Tsukune-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:25.41,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.54,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:28.94,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.52,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.99,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master is in that mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.71,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukune-san, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:46.02,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! It's dangerous for you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:47.50,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:51.67,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Tsukune-san, hurry and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:58.46,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kurumu-chan, Yukari-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:04.67,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, you were pretty good for a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:09.87,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you, you can move pretty well, despite your {\i1}load{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:14.36,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so. It's the first time I felt jealous that you were a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.89,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a big-breasted comrade is so troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:22.31,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it already, but we have bigger enemies to fight against, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.87,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Shirayuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.49,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:56.94,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, these are what's controlling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:00.51,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Those demons...and Ruby-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:04.95,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:17.70,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,You are... You are... the Master, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:24.43,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, please release Ruby-san! At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:46.14,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do I have to deal with these small fry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.85,Yukihime,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we defeat them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:54.68,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,If we suffer together, this is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:57.39,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys really saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.59,Yukihime,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:02.07,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:06.30,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumu-san, Shirayuki-san, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.50,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Moka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:14.67,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san, we understand! We'll get off the hill immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.67,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't trespass here ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:19.59,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:25.37,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?! Whatever you say to her now is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:37.14,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall receive punishment for hurting the Witches' Hill!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.15,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.02,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Ruby-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.00,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.02,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukune-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.36,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:47.98,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,If Ruby-san does these things, no one will ever be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:51.76,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! At least for the sake of the Master, I'll-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:55.55,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? The Master isn't even here anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:59.76,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,What idiotic nonsense! The Master is inside the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:05.01,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, the Master inside the mansion is already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.45,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:17.52,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.88,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:23.36,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:28.20,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have became foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:33.42,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,What I've been doing is the same as the humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:36.67,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:44.00,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me... I am making you alone again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:49.61,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,My dear Ruby, I will always be with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.45,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,Always...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:58.54,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san, you should have known as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:01.84,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,That the Master is no longer here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.00,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,You just didn't want to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.49,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings of denial...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:13.12,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,The other Ruby-san... no, the Ruby inside you... created an image of her within yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:16.51,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:23.24,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.98,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... don't, Ruby-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.84,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:39.66,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,If she uses that forbidden magic, she'll never return to her original form again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.39,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.79,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:53.93,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.79,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:05.03,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone should die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.10,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being too rash, Ruby-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:14.31,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,What can we do? She can no longer go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:16.56,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:22.23,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:23.60,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukune-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:24.91,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,My wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:25.62,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Wand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.74,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Please throw me my wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:28.67,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,That one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.11,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:31.54,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:32.89,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:33.73,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:44.60,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Moka-san is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:52.97,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool, did you think you would be able to defeat me with just this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:55.65,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,This magic is not just powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:04.57,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,The current me is able to absorb the strength of other living things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:09.48,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,In others words, right now my powers are just like those of a vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:12.33,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Moka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:16.84,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Worrying is useless.  Leave it to Yukari!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:20.98,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyrical Magical: Happy Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.64,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy it, Mizore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.76,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance, Moka-san! Take her wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:31.76,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,We witches can't use magic without a wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:37.61,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if she'll revert back... but please, Moka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:41.83,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san... Please save Ruby-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:47.10,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right... this idiot is worrying about her as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.67,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:54.60,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...Everyone just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:57.77,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,Revert back to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.04,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Ruby's favorite thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:18.57,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:21.43,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm.....Ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.34,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:24.66,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.39,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! This Witches' Hill....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.57,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:35.43,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:03.30,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we couldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:06.03,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had been able to hang on longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.13,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't Tsukune's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:14.34,HawtCatGirl,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry for making you guys wait so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:17.75,HawtCatGirl,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I got tons of delicious-looking fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.15,HawtCatGirl,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? It's already time to go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:26.38,Gin,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:28.10,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.79,All,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:33.04,Gin,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with this gloomy atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:36.78,Gin,,0000,0000,0000,,Your club leader just finished his supplementary lessons, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:38.45,Gin,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should be more cheerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:40.45,Gin,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:42.49,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:44.65,All,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.58,Gin,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:47.90,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:50.75,Gin,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:53.62,Gin,,0000,0000,0000,,I only found this girl just recently by the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:57.02,Gin,,0000,0000,0000,,Like she was possessed with protecting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:02.34,Tsukune,,0000,0000,0000,,Like she was protecting something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The road's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was actually such a beautiful hill in this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:35.27,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is a sunflower garden that has been endearingly important to the witches for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:37.77,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll also take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:41.03,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always, always take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:45.50,Master,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go back, to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:46.04,Ruby,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:33.18,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, summer vacation is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.18,0:24:35.72,Yukari,,0000,0000,0000,,Being emotional about it doesn't help!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:38.38,Yukihime,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I make a whirlwind for your summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.38,0:24:40.29,Kurumu,,0000,0000,0000,,Noo, anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.29,0:24:42.36,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, New School Term and A Vampire
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.36,0:24:44.29,Moka,,0000,0000,0000,,And a kappuchu for you!
